description:
Explore the intriguing depths of Rorschach, the most controversial character from Alan Moore's groundbreaking graphic novel: "Watchmen."

Despite being designed as a warning rather than a role model, Rorschach became an icon. His unyielding stance on justice, even in the face of overwhelming odds, challenges our traditional understanding of heroism.

If you liked this check out my main channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCz1fTbwui7o5aDZ6W1dOLTQ
title: Alan Moore said WHAT About Rorschach?! (Literature Devil)
